Zephyr RTOS
-----------

    Project: Zephyr RTOS
    Origin:  https://zephyrproject.org/
    License: Apache-2.0

    9p4z is a Zephyr module: it builds against the Zephyr kernel,
    Bluetooth (L2CAP), and networking APIs.  No Zephyr source is
    vendored into this repository.


Design lineage
--------------

The 9P2000 protocol is the work of Bell Labs (Plan 9).  9p4z is an
independent implementation from the published protocol
specification; no Plan 9 source code is incorporated.


